{"tid":452351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"70歲患癌婆婆哭斥：每個月得千幾蚊傷殘津貼養全家！","createTime":"2017-10-30T06:19:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-30T10:42:16.000Z","uid":1886,"like":36,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"b2f68041f1325cd25aa144ac166d80e3e36b7969","tid":452351,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T06:19:02.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】「我當時話畀自己知，唔可以跌低，因為我要一個人撐3個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」，說出這句話的人，不是彪形大漢，而是一名曾中風、患乳癌及淋巴腺癌的70歲婆婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。個性開朗的任太，表面上看不到傷痕，但原來曾兩度企圖自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，兒子3年前患肝癌離世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，女兒自小患自閉症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，丈夫7年前患腦癌後半癱需照顧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但任太向來只獲每月千多元的傷殘津貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，所有支援皆來自非牟利機構<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，「完全冇政府部門幫我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，係我自己搵機構幫我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171030/large/30la8p03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171030%2Flarge%2F30la8p03.jpg&h=bcd257e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">半身癱瘓的任生現年82歲，一直由任太照顧。</span><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171030/20198892\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171030%2F20198892&d=AGvHFC3Ye9q1nZzXwKH0%2F%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=6c34c33b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171030%2F20198892&h=3602007f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171030/20198892</a></div>"},{"pid":"0508508f81ce9e780f2dc00f095b24d894a2fc16","tid":452351,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T06:20:49.000Z","msg":"任太一家皆有長期病患，失去唯一家庭經濟支柱的兒子，她現時以年長殘疾人士身份照顧82歲的半癱丈夫，同時亦有一名38歲患嚴重自閉症的女兒，「我想人幫，未有機構幫我時，我得自己一個」。任太現只獲每月1,695元的普通傷殘津貼及「食老本」，丈夫曾申請傷殘津貼但不獲批<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。統計處資料顯示，殘疾人士的年齡中位數為72歲，較整體人口年齡中位數高出30歲，越高齡的人士，殘疾普遍率亦越高，70歲及以上人士的殘疾普遍率最高，達42.6%。"},{"pid":"45b479a38aab26548ab81fe101a246215343d802","tid":452351,"uid":32425,"like":63,"dislike":75,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T06:21:30.000Z","msg":"賤格小小講句<br />\n活了七十幾年人<br />\n後生時無儲蓄<br />\n以為有間公屋可以安享晚年<br />\n仲諗住靠政府？"},{"pid":"a306ba5fdfe1bcf5961fe8d6f75927d8e77197cf","tid":452351,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T06:22:20.000Z","msg":"任太已屆七旬，本應享兒孫福，2008年卻突然中風，2009年患乳癌及淋巴腺癌，丈夫於2010年確診腦癌並半身癱瘓，經濟支柱的兒子前年因肝癌離世，女兒早於兩歲確診自閉症需人照顧，任太曾同時照顧3人，面對長達近10年的家庭夢魘，她雖能樂觀面對困境，卻坦言曾兩度企圖自殺。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171030/large/30la8p01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171030%2Flarge%2F30la8p01.jpg&h=fef7509b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"> 任太談起經歷時不禁落淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，並指一家人齊齊整整合照已成歷史。</span></div><br />\n<br />\n第一次萌生自殺念頭是女兒年幼時，因自閉症沒有自控能力，任太亦面臨一連串困境，「周圍走，無論人哋飲過未，都搶人可樂飲，俾人話我唔識湊女，我又同時面對升職嘅掙扎同經濟問題，當時係第一次坐上天台想自殺」。第二次萌生自殺念頭是2009年時，她患癌期間屢受折磨，家人照顧長期病患者力有不逮，她自己亦苦不堪言，衝到窗旁企圖自殺。<br />\n<br />\n事隔多年，她自己亦成為照顧長期病患者的角色，「我好厚面皮周圍搵人幫，政府係莫名其妙、袖手旁觀」，自兒子離世後，她只靠非牟利機構的上門服務，包括替丈夫洗澡及物理治療，「我係想佢（丈夫）住院舍，但又唔捨得，我哋感情好」。"},{"pid":"0b3b5543e0a45023ff26230f30025daeb61bba4e","tid":452351,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T06:23:03.000Z","msg":"協助任太的立法會議員張超雄指，「任太訪問時表面好樂觀，但其實生活困難，一直只諗住自己要撐住，但佢自己都年紀大又有病」，他斥政府是孤寒財主，「政府唔想開展呢類經營性開支，結果將責任推畀機構，但其實民間機構已無法負荷」。"},{"pid":"446db4711f7ccfbb8814b008b634f8c5681921fc","tid":452351,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T06:26:43.000Z","msg":"咩事全家都癌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30fe6ceedfae4710ed8e989534fa039828da533e","tid":452351,"uid":11148,"like":49,"dislike":20,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T06:32:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩事全家都癌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n細女自閉,證明窮撚既劣質基因就算生下一代<br />\n<br />\n個天都會收你皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"647ca8fe424fc0137974f93902ab32cc39a9ac28","tid":452351,"uid":65887,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T06:32:33.000Z","msg":"攞唔到綜援 長生津<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁係政府角度你仲未夠窮"},{"pid":"beb987dff2942e0829fab5bf885e57149d9c1093","tid":452351,"uid":101328,"like":60,"dislike":3,"score":57,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T06:32:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>賤格小小講句<br />\n活了七十幾年人<br />\n後生時無儲蓄<br />\n以為有間公屋可以安享晚年<br />\n仲諗住靠政府？</blockquote><br />\n你咁講又真係賤格左D喔。。。。儲蓄呢家野冇病冇痛就話啫，屋企有咩事可能一次過冇左一大半。"},{"pid":"e3cb64627f4685c3dbb29846a19b2337414c3f30","tid":452351,"uid":11148,"like":1,"dislike":19,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T06:34:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>賤格小小講句<br />\n活了七十幾年人<br />\n後生時無儲蓄<br />\n以為有間公屋可以安享晚年<br />\n仲諗住靠政府？</blockquote><br />\n你咁講又真係賤格左D喔。。。。儲蓄呢家野冇病冇痛就話啫，<span style=\"color: red;\">屋企有咩事可能一次過冇左一大半</span>。</blockquote><br />\n窮人唔識買保險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d9a89734396b6598ae492809d1036c15b9fb4e1","tid":452351,"uid":38666,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T06:37:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>賤格小小講句<br />\n活了七十幾年人<br />\n後生時無儲蓄<br />\n以為有間公屋可以安享晚年<br />\n仲諗住靠政府？</blockquote><br />\n你咁講又真係賤格左D喔。。。。儲蓄呢家野冇病冇痛就話啫，<span style=\"color: red;\">屋企有咩事可能一次過冇左一大半</span>。</blockquote><br />\n窮人唔識買保險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一日三差都有困難 仲有錢買保險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bede171d9a9280448bbd58db9dc8e441453b828","tid":452351,"uid":35783,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T06:37:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>賤格小小講句<br />\n活了七十幾年人<br />\n後生時無儲蓄<br />\n以為有間公屋可以安享晚年<br />\n仲諗住靠政府？</blockquote><br />\n你咁講又真係賤格左D喔。。。。儲蓄呢家野冇病冇痛就話啫，<span style=\"color: red;\">屋企有咩事可能一次過冇左一大半</span>。</blockquote><br />\n窮人唔識買保險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買左唔包呢可能"},{"pid":"622c100b0fcc8b3e67992d2c827358aae2075c58","tid":452351,"uid":82411,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T06:38:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>賤格小小講句<br />\n活了七十幾年人<br />\n後生時無儲蓄<br />\n以為有間公屋可以安享晚年<br />\n仲諗住靠政府？</blockquote><br />\n你咁講又真係賤格左D喔。。。。儲蓄呢家野冇病冇痛就話啫，<span style=\"color: red;\">屋企有咩事可能一次過冇左一大半</span>。</blockquote><br />\n窮人唔識買保險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係你有事 你梗係咁講啦 保險保到你奶野果一下姐<br />\n你之後完全做唔到野 傷殘又一定多一筆洗費<br />\n保險真係COVER曬? 如果邊間COVER到咁多 介紹我 我去買 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c53843ccfc071ad9a51f8ba88db107e22797f135","tid":452351,"uid":39796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sco